  "description": "Use this skill when writing, debugging, or optimizing SAQL queries in CRM Analytics \u2014 covering pipeline syntax, aggregation, windowing functions (rank, dense_rank, moving_average), cogroup joins, rollup subtotals, piggyback queries, and REST API execution. NOT for SOQL, standard Salesforce reports, SQL databases, or any non-CRM Analytics query language.",
